==English==

===Etymology===
[[bi-]] + [[month]] + [[-ly]]

===Adverb===
'''bimonthly'''

# Occurring [[once]] every two months.
# [[Twice]] every [[month]]; [[semimonthly]].

====Usage notes====
Because of the ambiguity of this word, it is best to avoid it. Instead, use ''twice a month'' or ''every two months'' as appropriate.

"Bimonthly" correctly refers an "every 2 months" occurance. "Every 2 weeks" should be termed "biweekly" or "semimonthly."

